proposals.title: Exclude Validator 1
proposals.description: Voting for exclusion of consortium member can also be implemented when seeing the list of all validators- this will then link to the page where a Vote for exclusion of consortium member can be started and the wallet address of that member who belongs to that Node ID is automatically filled for the proposal.
